		"name": "RentNest Backend API",
		"description": "## Introduction\n\n**RentNest** is a secure RESTful API for a property rental platform where landlords can list properties, tenants can browse and request rentals, and payments are processed securely using Stripe.\n\nThe API follows REST principles, JWT authentication, role-based authorization, and consistent response structures.\n\n**Base URL**\n\n``` http\nhttps://rentnest-seven.vercel.app\n\n ```",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "55043461",
